{"tid":2047447,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子遭跪頸亡 警不提死因  簡浩名轟查三周無果︰香港真係咁落後？","createTime":"2020-06-02T06:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T10:36:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f99d2897968188fa10035adaee47a57d097f2790","tid":2047447,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:18:44.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200602/TKACGFMJYTJVEVKF4IORGCR4Z4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200602%2FTKACGFMJYTJVEVKF4IORGCR4Z4%2F&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbZo9Jm%2BrpizTNr1X5Fgg%2Fao%3D&h=df36a6bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200602%2FTKACGFMJYTJVEVKF4IORGCR4Z4%2F&h=005a6268\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200602/TKACGFMJYTJVEVKF4IORGCR4Z4/</a><br />\n<br />\n男子遭跪頸亡 警不提死因 <br />\n簡浩名轟查三周無果︰香港真係咁落後？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國警察跪頸致黑人男子死亡事件引起軒然大波，涉事警員被控謀殺，但本港上月初亦有南亞裔男子在尖沙嘴遭警員壓頸制服後送院不治。社福界選委簡浩名去信追究警暴，日前接獲警方回信，僅指案件仍在調查，簡浩名質疑警方故意拖延令事件不了了之。此外，上周三警方在全港多區大搜捕，一名19歲青年於旺角遭警員以盾牌壓頸拘捕，他已求助區議員，誓言要向警方討回公道。<br />\n<br />\n記者：江子堯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NIQRPNRVCHFTDWPF2ZX7R5U264.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNIQRPNRVCHFTDWPF2ZX7R5U264.jpg&h=d48a95e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡浩名早前去信追究南亞男子遭警壓頸制服後死亡的案件。<br />\n<br />\n簡浩名早前在區議員及人權組織成員陪同下，就南亞裔男子在尖沙嘴遭警員壓頸後死亡的案件，到灣仔警察總部抗議警。。。。。。。。。。。。指正調查事件，稍後向死因裁判官呈交報告，但未有公佈死者死因，或其國籍及身份，以及警方是否已把死訊通知死者家人等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TWFRU4XDPAI34QMZT2YBUPBR2E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTWFRU4XDPAI34QMZT2YBUPBR2E.jpg&h=9d3709ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對港美處理同類警暴手法迥異，簡發帖問「香港人命是否咁賤？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZJSJ5M4YQ3AXYEMIEN6DOMEFXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZJSJ5M4YQ3AXYEMIEN6DOMEFXM.jpg&h=7659c1b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方調查三周後仍未交代遭壓頸南亞男子的死因。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K3UX7NZ2C56ESII74AMCUWLLW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK3UX7NZ2C56ESII74AMCUWLLW4.jpg&h=7ff7d093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大學生Peter上周亦被警員以盾壓頸制服。資料圖片<br />\n盾壓後頸 男生誓討公道<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：人權組織斥警高層默許有罪不罰<br />\n<br />\n簡直斥警方「回信內容係冇意思！」他認為警方至今仍未公佈死因。。。。。。。。。。。為至少應把涉案警員停職候查，以示公正，又要求警方馬上「止警暴、制警亂」。<br />\n<br />\n事發上月7日，油尖警區軍裝人員巡經彌敦道時，追截一名有酒氣的南亞裔男子，他涉刑毀私家車及電。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。質疑做法非常有問題。該名男子被制服後不適送院，翌日死亡，警方事後稱使用適當武力將事主制服。<br />\n<br />\n此外，上周三多區示威活動中警方拘捕近400人，其中被捕的19歲大學生Peter憶述，當日下午他只是與。。。。。。。。。。。。。。唞唔到氣」，幸好被壓頸的時間短，否則後果嚴重，及後他被警方以涉嫌公眾地方行為不檢拘捕帶署。<br />\n<br />\nPeter認為警方以不合理方式去壓制市民，使用過份。。。。。。。。。。。。。對待手無寸鐵的市民用過份武力，已違反國際人權。"},{"pid":"1b0df4f8031adb0d88f02e87878fa8ddb06324fd","tid":2047447,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401d0b1287259c21f6f74ae8b0bbf5e53b5eca76","tid":2047447,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e6d028c0c595dd87596befd9b007c87814df84","tid":2047447,"uid":83328,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:25:29.000Z","msg":"接受現實啦<br />\n<br />\n香港制度已經係第三世界level 啦<br />\n<br />\n應該係仲衰過"},{"pid":"f38b7e5bae5cbb9fb5cb51da59f6674c74c97af5","tid":2047447,"uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7