"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f38b7e5bae5cbb9fb5cb51da59f6674c74c97af5","tid":2047447,"uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:26:38.000Z","msg":"林鄭：睇下美國點處理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:28:40.000Z","msg":"炳強 : 衰婆收口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:20:28.000Z","msg":"柒婆真係唔提都仲好<br />\n一提個結果嘅話藍屍都要番屋企匿埋避一避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9234d08c2d84ab7ab1adb001cc39730e41bf78","tid":2047447,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a376d3f56bad877faa9b4ddffa5e80279cf0fa7","tid":2047447,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:21:38.000Z","msg":"簡浩名立即變黃, 得左"},{"pid":"86ab71ffee3bd718614162513da750a60708d1d1","tid":2047447,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a376d3f56bad877faa9b4ddffa5e80279cf0fa7","tid":2047447,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:21:38.000Z","msg":"簡浩名立即變黃, 得左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:22:28.000Z","msg":"佢唔係熱狗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab6da93d37b63de7155c0a35a45e6eddbf22065","tid":2047447,"uid":263484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:24:41.000Z","msg":"問下毛漢啦<br />\n佢係再出發大聯盟丫嘛"},{"pid":"31f3e16a49518cf53478a40c19d33e6dfd9ebf45","tid":2047447,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:38:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">植根港百年 巴漢被拒入籍 <br />\n入境處原因：沒有近親是中國人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n//巴基斯坦裔的簡浩名在港土生土長，家族早於1912年移居至此，植根三代人，甘願放棄巴籍，申領特區護照時卻屢遭留難。入境處以他「沒有近親是中國人」為由，拒絕接納其入籍申請。「我家族喺香港一百年，點解我唔可以拎特區護照？」//<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20121213/18099692\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20121213%2F18099692&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbZo9Jm%2BrpizTNr1X5Fgg%2Fao%3D&h=ec9fd643\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20121213%2F18099692&h=37bdad73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20121213/18099692</a><br />\n<br />\n中國一直提倡「血濃於水」、「炎黃子孫」，以血緣民族主義綁架香港人既定義，透過血緣強逼香港人成為中國人。依種落伍同種族主義既血統主義思維，甚至成為政策。同香港無關係無貢獻既支那人可以自出自入黎攞綜緩，扎根三代、家族參加過香港保衛戰既香港人就連護照都冇得拎。<br />\n<br />\n所以點解少數族裔、非華裔香港人應該支持本土主義同香港獨立。因為本土主義就係要將香港人同中國既關係割裂，將香港人身份同中國血統既關係割裂。唔再以血統定義香港人，「香港人身份」由每個香港人既價值、認同以及共同經營所定義。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4JpHsfH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4JpHsfH.jpg&h=e0a8ee49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04bb1af5262e25b59011100ba807b5ba645b7478","tid":2047447,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:38:46.000Z","msg":"暴政下出暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f96913f6741f5bc6452b9f21b9fd11725be737","tid":2047447,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9325e7137939e618878a232e2979b1f8f11c07a8","tid":2047447,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:39:41.000Z","msg":"#brownlivematter"},{"pid":"f47ea1fb1cba9a26c881cdef57406323943b5b08","tid":2047447,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:40:29.000Z","msg":"陰功囉"},{"pid":"b5c55435f08a47a3bd4ff7a85c2c7b08b6bfdf7a","tid":2047447,"uid":297